     &lt;span class=&#34;token string&#34;&gt;&#34;selectedIconPath&#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;token string&#34;&gt;&#34;assets/tabs/icon1.png&#34;&lt;/span&gt;
