     &lt;span class=&#34;token string&#34;&gt;&#34;pagePath&#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;token string&#34;&gt;&#34;pages/index/index&#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
